parameters.name: model_ids
parameters.description: Seller SKU of this model, model_ids length information needs to be no more than 100 characters

parameters.name: seller_stock
parameters.description: Seller stock (Please notice that stock(including seller stock and preorder Stock) should be updated with the interface of updating model stock)

parameters.name: dimension
parameters.description: The dimension of this model. If don't set the dimension of this model, will use the dimension of item by default

parameters.name: package_length
parameters.description: The length of package for this model, the unit is CM

parameters.name: package_width
parameters.description: The width of package for this model, the unit is CM

parameters.name: package_height
parameters.description: The height of package for this model, the unit is CM

parameters.name: is_pre_order
parameters.description: Whether the model is pre order

parameters.name: days_to_ship
parameters.description: Days to ship. Please get the days_to_ship range from the get_dts_limit API

response_fields.name: error
response_fields.description: Indicate error type if hit error. Empty if no error happened

response_fields.name: message
response_fields.description: Indicate error details if hit error. Empty if no error happened

response_fields.name: warning
response_fields.description: Indicate warning details if hit warning. Empty if no warning happened

response_fields.name: request_id
response_fields.description: The identifier for an API request for error tracking

response_fields.name: item_id
response_fields.description: Shopee's unique identifier for an item
